data.description: Spectacular Bay view with an amazing panoramic view of The Miami Port. Direct view of the The Kayesa Center Arena. Walking distance to Bayside park, shops, and restaurants. This unit has porcelain tile flooring, open kitchen, granite countertops, floors, high impact windows and big balcony with access from the bedroom and the living room. The building has two pools, hot top, sand volleyball court, fitness center, party room, and barbecue area. Unit has 1 parking space in the 8th floor that gives an easy access to the unit.
